Package: anvil
Version: 2.2.7
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Culpur Defense Engineering <jyoung@culpur.net>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.35), ca-certificates, git
Recommends: nodejs (>= 18), npm
Description: Anvil AI coding assistant
 Anvil is a full-featured AI coding assistant with multi-provider support
 (Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, xAI, Ollama), encrypted vault for API keys,
 AnvilHub package ecosystem, and deep shell integration.
 .
 After install, run: anvil --setup
Homepage: https://anvilhub.culpur.net
